{"tid":49343,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"［懷舊/又到聖誕］水滸歷險私服","createTime":"2016-12-21T15:35:25.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-07T10:49:00.000Z","uid":26753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"323d02ec138998eeecc70ca70a139840998013b2","tid":49343,"uid":26753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T15:35:25.000Z","msg":"就到聖誕 如無意外又出活動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n<br />\n依家開始已經有雙倍泡點 幾日就砌到set雀裝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n反正聖誕冇野做 不如入黎吹下水 抽下水 打副本 懷舊一下啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n新手入game可以搵 <span style=\"color: red;\">三點四 劉備 賞金獵人</span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n可以睇下個舊post 有齊攻略 唔明既入game再問<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n[懷舊]水滸歷險Online 私服<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/4809/page/1?ref=ios\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/4809/page/1?ref=ios</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n游戲名稱：Hehe水滸歷險 <br />\n官方網站：<a href=\"http://hehe108.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhehe108.com&d=DgJ1U%2FQ4SkTgvWt%2FEKlm%2B2N6obqfy%2FNc7jg2IsrTbnE%3D&h=e9d5aa8f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">hehe108.com</a> <br />\n官方論壇：<a href=\"http://hehe108.com/forum\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhehe108.com%2Fforum&d=DgJ1U%2FQ4SkTgvWt%2FEKlm%2B2N6obqfy%2FNc7jg2IsrTbnE%3D&h=6a9cb26b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">hehe108.com/forum</a> <br />\n下載地址：<a href=\"http://drive.google.com/file/d/0B3e8X4t1CJVEOHlzdGlzWW9qX1U/view\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fdrive.google.com%2Ffile%2Fd%2F0B3e8X4t1CJVEOHlzdGlzWW9qX1U%2Fview&d=DgJ1U%2FQ4SkTgvWt%2FEKlm%2B2N6obqfy%2FNc7jg2IsrTbnE%3D&h=348e848c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">drive.google.com/file/d/0B3e8X4t1CJVEOHlzdGlzWW9qX1U/view</a> <br /